::Hot Rod::

Hot Rod hab been lisening to the conversation between Prowl, Iron
Rapter, and Feline.
"Whats going on?" He asked.

::DrillBit::

DrillBit ran back out side the cave, shooting at all enemys. He spoted
KitKat, and ran up to her. He gave her a quick kiss, on the cheek.
"Welcome to the party." He said, in sarcasm.
